{"tid":586951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉鳴煒：青年問題非派錢解決　否則「開張cheque就得」","createTime":"2018-03-10T04:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T05:22:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ca8489f669099cf36f51cb68579e679fc7615af3","tid":586951,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180310/s00001/8b612456f6a86509d90fe2317b0410c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180310%2Fs00001%2F8b612456f6a86509d90fe2317b0410c3.jpg&h=b87eeac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因應財政預算案被指未能惠及所有人，政府提出關愛基金的「補漏拾遺」方案，研究擴大「N無人士」範圍，包括薪酬不高又毋須交稅、剛畢業的青年人。青年事務委員會主席劉鳴煒表明不認同派錢，直指如果派錢能解決問題，就不用政府施政。<br />\n<br />\n劉鳴煒今早出席港台節目時，被問到關愛基金將青年人納入「N無人士」，他表示外界對派錢出現很多爭議，甚至很多人贊成派錢給「N無」的青年人，但他表明不同意，認為尚有很多青少年問題不能以錢解決，例如學業壓力、自殺問題等，反問「係咪真係派3000、6000、1萬元就解決到」？<br />\n<br />\n他指相信政府知道很多問題不是靠派錢，「如果這麼容易其實不需要施政，開張cheque(支票)就得」。<br />\n<br />\n青年事務委員會早前舉行105場針對青少年的諮詢會，劉鳴煒指出相比置業問題，15至25歲的青少年最關心都是教育。他說很多問題與教育相關，認為青少年不能實踐全能發展。<br />\n<br />\n針對政府早前推行的「青年委員自薦試行計劃」，劉表示反應熱烈，超過500名自薦人士參加；又形容自薦人士的質素很高，包括表達能力及對議題的認識等。他期望選出的3人未來能在委員會有所發揮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180310/s00001/1520652254509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180310%2Fs00001%2F1520652254509&d=RRtZKrgL7KbMpQD%2BJNyOfP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=108f4427\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180310%2Fs00001%2F1520652254509&h=7d3f9b77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180310/s00001/1520652254509</a>"},{"pid":"3c23659d9f3c60f275529586944072a9d96b240e","tid":586951,"uid":87780,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:27:17.000Z","msg":"又嚟扮青年騎劫青年"},{"pid":"af96a2911041cebbd2f14f39bbfa1537f7d54245","tid":586951,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:27:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"822e7bf11e41484cf29dd3dcb7aeb94a5c44cf37","tid":586951,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:27:57.000Z","msg":"荷蘭銀行支票"},{"pid":"d90f7695f88ea2721e7b73c3eb0331b66dab0f4c","tid":586951,"uid":38671,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:28:22.000Z","msg":"係呀, 開張cheque就得<br />\n<br />\n而家根本係錢既問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee283ab254bed1c88822df36e155cc87ac62fe9","tid":586951,"uid":31637,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"你試下比張十萬支票要一個反共既人收口呀<br />\n連登排撚住隊收口, 分分鐘會頂爛市, 最後收5豪都收口"},{"pid":"1c79a3130b72bc2f293f5fc012eb57bb6c64e4bd","tid":586951,"uid":138834,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:35:57.000Z","msg":"原則上冇錯呀開cheque解決到大部分年青人問題<br />\n問題係，政府開張dishonoured cheque呢"},{"pid":"3814161891363d1b792080eb200811c94ae6f3a1","tid":586951,"uid":105033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:39:28.000Z","msg":"佢仲青年？ 死番去佢老母個閪到再出生啦"},{"pid":"329b7607aad3f5cedb39b0fa52714094664387e9","tid":586951,"uid":119695,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:41:32.000Z","msg":"如果條友係基層出身，咪一樣會屌政府唔派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5265ff7d218a8607d1342e00a9150f16b16f3719","tid":586951,"uid":33643,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:43:17.000Z","msg":"你俾6000蚊後生仔去下旅行，放鬆下都自殺少幾個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96ce2491cdd466021d28339189262e7efb8fb77","tid":586951,"uid":51753,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:44:55.000Z","msg":"真係開張CHEQUE就得<br />\n<br />\n一係就正苦包機一年包一次日本/泡國來回機票<br />\n散下心又冇咁大怨氣好似係"},{"pid":"2bc4fa70bb1d61ab9159601f65a4b0a18ba9020b","tid":586951,"uid":6752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:45:05.000Z","msg":"40幾歲都係青年"},{"pid":"e94685a99bb0283863b698043752b09cdd9b6372","tid":586951,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:45:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0a419ca585f251998ef181579e40d49793833e8","tid":586951,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:46:55.000Z","msg":"你叫你老豆每個後生仔派1皮即刻無人反共"},{"pid":"0e4c0e8abd881d36f693293ce8c61a0da82f7cde","tid":586951,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:47:01.000Z","msg":"只可以話<br />\n海洋公園飛同cheque揀<br />\n我會揀cheque囉<br />\n屍政？屍俾大財團咋喎"},{"pid":"bdce095e7dc23cc796119f7cf3361522e76e5167","tid":586951,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:48:09.000Z","msg":"買到樓既支票一張就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea93f5f9b9421ee4058443aed1576ad23d5d4d4","tid":586951,"uid":127988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:48:26.000Z","msg":"大劉: 你咁撚白痴, 以後唔使返華置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ddce0a391b00d2df8eca3dd6c5b159c8ef35b0","tid":586951,"uid":99493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T04:48:32.000Z","msg":"又斷章取義<br />\n<br />\n鬼唔知派錢解決唔到所有問題<br />\n而家派錢只係安撫民心<br />\n<br />\n當社會大部分問題政府沒有心去解決<br />\n市民只想拿一點安慰"},{"pid":"c96c8bdc2eb2d60fe5eec5f8e1f64eab5e097c3e","tid":586951,"uid":23786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:20:55.000Z","msg":"一年派兩皮俾人去日本，包冇人屌政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b24036aa02189855b4ffd257d6039f796034b30","tid":586951,"uid":2914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:22:13.000Z","msg":"仲有人理依條傻鳩<img src=\"/a